  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Automated Node-based Farm Simulator</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/dbec0deb3068baa104f2f7f63610424b.poster.avif?t=1769106439\" width=616 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/dbec0deb3068baa104f2f7f63610424b.webm?t=1769106439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/dbec0deb3068baa104f2f7f63610424b.mp4?t=1769106439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Do you like farming simulators? Automation? Strategy? Roguelites? Cozy vibes? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can find it all here! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple and Relaxing Complexity</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/56423637eea6189029f6cd314656ea32.poster.avif?t=1769106439\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/56423637eea6189029f6cd314656ea32.webm?t=1769106439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/56423637eea6189029f6cd314656ea32.mp4?t=1769106439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>It's simple. Just connect nodes and watch your farm grow! Mechanics may be simple to get into but the possibilities are limited only by your imagination. Experiment with the nodes, and find your own best way to maximize the profit! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strategy and Resource Management</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/f89459a538436edc88b064d751843419.poster.avif?t=1769106439\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/f89459a538436edc88b064d751843419.webm?t=1769106439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/f89459a538436edc88b064d751843419.mp4?t=1769106439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Prices in the veggie market are constantly changing. Adapt your farm to the market and make it work for you! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Replayable Roguelite Experience</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy new islands, discover new nodes, and move your progress between farms in a procedurally generated replayable experience! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Coming Soon!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make sure to <strong>WISHLIST</strong> the game and maybe join my  server if you are interested!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Automated Node-based Farm Simulator</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/dbec0deb3068baa104f2f7f63610424b.poster.avif?t=1769106439\" width=616 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/dbec0deb3068baa104f2f7f63610424b.webm?t=1769106439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/dbec0deb3068baa104f2f7f63610424b.mp4?t=1769106439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Do you like farming simulators? Automation? Strategy? Roguelites? Cozy vibes? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can find it all here! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple and Relaxing Complexity</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/56423637eea6189029f6cd314656ea32.poster.avif?t=1769106439\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/56423637eea6189029f6cd314656ea32.webm?t=1769106439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/56423637eea6189029f6cd314656ea32.mp4?t=1769106439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>It's simple. Just connect nodes and watch your farm grow! Mechanics may be simple to get into but the possibilities are limited only by your imagination. Experiment with the nodes, and find your own best way to maximize the profit! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strategy and Resource Management</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/f89459a538436edc88b064d751843419.poster.avif?t=1769106439\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/f89459a538436edc88b064d751843419.webm?t=1769106439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738990/extras/f89459a538436edc88b064d751843419.mp4?t=1769106439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Prices in the veggie market are constantly changing. Adapt your farm to the market and make it work for you! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Replayable Roguelite Experience</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy new islands, discover new nodes, and move your progress between farms in a procedurally generated replayable experience! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Coming Soon!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make sure to <strong>WISHLIST</strong> the game and maybe join my  server if you are interested!</p>",
